= Overview =

Issues for PKI are currently maintained in [https://pagure.io/dogtagpki/issues Pagure]. Since github hosts it's own issues page, it will be easier to track and close issues.

= Advantages of github issues =

* Easier to track & user-friendly
* Attracts more public attention
* Possibility for more contributors
* Issues can be referenced from comments/commits/PRs
* Syncs easily once we move away from Gerrithub to Github Pull Requests. Refer [[Gerrit_vs_GitHub_Pull_Request|here]]


= Reason for migrating away from Pagure = 
 
* Difficult to track issues
* Every time a commit is made, pagure URL needs to be copied and pasted in the commit message

